派</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱狗其實都好無恥<br />\n被全世界圍屌時, 就話自己係反共派, 叫人唔好「反共派日日互屌」<br />\n到唔屌熱狗啦, 佢熱狗就日日屌人清算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f33d5efcdf7716f9ee3e813d19334ef8277c1e","tid":299090,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:51:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打自己人最勁不嬲都係基因來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個係「自己人」？<br />\n<br />\n你講清楚先"},{"pid":"e070b2f3b8785ae7f1201f951f11076c48e7aaee","tid":299090,"uid":123187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"&quot;惟有建立一個有行動力既革命政黨&quot;<br />\n<br />\n成篇野都正常, 但呢句突顯閣下底裡的無知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩年代, 仲革命?  人去到今日已經同往時好唔同啦, 現實, 聰明, 自我..  今日孫中山係度都無人會啋佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7204bf3e6077581b8c8ec9079b0db8ee518b52b","tid":299090,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:18:26.000Z","msg":"而家已經冇人識屌共, 個個都淨係識互相清算, 你睇下依個台D post 就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793969df41608ebe278c8d2789a39c3c20f4161a","tid":299090,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T03:09:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家已經冇人識屌共, 個個都淨係識互相清算, 你睇下依個台D post 就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咪去時事台屌共匪囉, 日日都大把人屌緊<br />\n<br />\n你條盲毛係咪入錯台呀？"},{"pid":"191c5753ae859231ce8065e00f11f1f048fb6d8b","tid":299090,"uid":32486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:13:29.000Z","msg":"又有新用字 反共派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d5cbba049c175f94dcb8612a7a391f0aab58c0","tid":299090,"uid":32486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"屌定唔屌<br />\n其實好簡單<br />\n<br />\n你望一望佢既政綱